thread.title: Sumeer Misra

author: Sumeer Misra
title: Sumeer Misra
text: My experience with Havealook has been sublime. They completed all tasks in a timely fashion, were upfront regarding costs and their scope of work and I am extremely happy with the finished product. And to top it all off, they were friendly and took time to explain any questions I had. I have already recommended them to other small business owners I know and can't thank them enough for all their hard work and professionalism.
